here's my config file for laythe. it's moving the planet. but it's not disrupting the the tidal lock.

doed anyone have any ideas?

    @Kopernicus:FINAL:NEEDS[Kopernicus]{    @Body[Laythe]    {        @Properties        {    %rotationPeriod = 216000    @ScienceValues            {        flyingLowDataValue = 5        flyingHighDataValue = 4.5                    landedDataValue = 4        inSpaceLowDataValue = 3        inSpaceHighDataValue = 2.5        recoveryValue = 3              }        }        @Orbit        {        %referenceBody = Sun    semiMajorAxis = 12711029575    inclination = 0        eccentricity = 0    longitudeOfAscendingNode = 0        }    }}
